This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image denoising. The use of convolutional neural networks also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The mention of synthetic data generation and optimization techniques could also place it in the multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories.
